text: Shaimaa Ahmed Khalaf Haridy (born 1 January 1991) is an Egyptian female weightlifter, competing in the +75 kg category and representing Egypt at international competitions. She competed at world championships, including at the 2015 World Weightlifting Championships. At the 2016 Summer Olympics she competed in the Women's +75 kg.
